HOW TO INSTALL
-------------------
To install run "pip install pyglobe" or "easy_install pyglobe".


EXAMPLE CODE
-------------------

import pyglobe

try:
	service = pyglobe.PyGlobe(uname='gzqloovr0', pin='21737796', msisdn='09178363916')
	service.sendSMS('Message through Globe Labs API')
except (PyGlobeInvalidServiceException, PyGlobeInvalidURLException, PyGlobeServerFaultException) as e:
	print "An error occurred: %s" % e
